## Hints for Future Agents
- BONUS BUG FIXED: `useEffect` at game-client.tsx:367 was overwriting
  currentRound with only rounds_public fields, wiping
  writing_team/turn_idx/turn_ends_at until the 2s poll backfilled.
  ~2s every page rendered as 'watcher' with "Turn 1 of 0". Merged the
